---
title: Soy and Lime Baked Salmon  with Teriyaki Noodles and Peanuts
description: Salmon is a delicate and flavoursome fish, perfect for absorbing flavours such as the soy sauce and zesty lime in this recipe. Paired with sticky teriyaki noodles loaded with veg, it's a real catch!
